query GetCoinDetails($coinId: ID!) {
  coinCreated(id: $coinId) {
    id
    name
    symbol
    coin
    uri
    payoutRecipient
    platformReferrer
    currency
    pool
    version
    caller {
      id
      blockNumber
      blockTimestamp
    }
    blockNumber
    blockTimestamp
    transactionHash
  }
}
